Validate a data frame with abstracts to construct vectpr of strings

abstracts2text.Rd

Validate a data frame with abstracts to construct vectpr of strings

Usage

abstracts2text(abstracts = NULL)

Arguments

abstracts

An object of the class abstracts (a data frame with abstracts) or a string vector with abstracts

Value

A validated character vector. The function check and encode characters in utf8 standard.

Examples

abstracts <- get_abstracts(lacsSample)
abstracts2text(abstracts)
